{"tid":2312910,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［正視聽］做狗好過做人","createTime":"2020-12-05T11:12:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T14:10:31.000Z","uid":375919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ab8b282e071ada99ce683184e0fa96b7c01feb4d","tid":2312910,"uid":375919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T11:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8u0N0cY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8u0N0cY.png&h=c014fa8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\">狗狗好去處2020｜旺角上海街室內串燒店設寵物餐單 $138狗食迴轉壽司＋$298三狗份量英式下午茶</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/petform/生活/好去處/detail/7JWDLXADYJCGJG26TFIAHYIRAY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fpetform%2F%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%2F%E5%A5%BD%E5%8E%BB%E8%99%95%2Fdetail%2F7JWDLXADYJCGJG26TFIAHYIRAY%2F&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w5q%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=804f4581\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fpetform%2F%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%2F%E5%A5%BD%E5%8E%BB%E8%99%95%2Fdetail%2F7JWDLXADYJCGJG26TFIAHYIRAY%2F&h=04a9703f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/petform/生活/好去處/detail/7JWDLXADYJCGJG26TFIAHYIRAY/</a><br />\n<br />\n萌寵英式下午茶（大$298）份量十足，兩至三隻狗狗分享都夠飽。每層食物均見心思，頂層是雞肉甘荀波波，中間有三文魚大阪燒，公司三文治是特製的寵物版，「麵包」是用雞肉及薯仔製成，不是普通白麵包。底層有南瓜雞肉雞軟骨丼飯，以及牛肉牛脷南瓜撻，再配以可愛Le Creuset茶碗盛着的南瓜湯，精緻可愛。毛孩迴轉壽司（$138）有12件，十款不同口味，「壽司飯」其實是雞肉條，鋪面的牛肉、帆立貝、魚等等全部是人類食用級數食材。毛孩串燒套餐（$108）連一個細小的串燒爐上桌，很有風味。<br />\n<br />\n店家的宗旨是「狗可以仲食得好過人類」，若果毛孩有食物敏感，預訂時可以預先跟店員溝通，套餐可以特別為毛孩轉換食材。店家還特別為毛孩預備了多套寵物衫、生日帽等等，可以免費借給毛孩拍照打卡。毛孩食得好，人類都唔弱。食堂早午市是港式冰室，食物種類多元化，價錢不貴。神級葱油雞扒飯（$52 連餐飲）以獨門秘方每日新鮮自家製，雞扒厚肉香口。晚市專做串燒，任食串燒由$198起，款式選擇多，配清酒或啤酒，大受歡迎。可惜的是店舖不算大，想帶毛孩去試試的父母記得一定要預先為毛孩訂位。"},{"pid":"52eaf43f096f0a0e3f976e5b3eb853a81de735d8","tid":2312910,"uid":375919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T11:15:55.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">店家的宗旨是「狗可以仲食得好過人類」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ad7cae68f0eac91c59b8e70567900fc5af3fdd6","tid":2312910,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T14:10:31.000Z","msg":"隻松鼠狗：<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}